


Please slide the picture of tiles and complete an original image.
This puzzle game allows you to make sliding puzzle games out of any picture you have on your iphone.
This game is simple but exciting!

■feature
・You can make your original puzzles
・You can edit your picture
・You can choose a normal mode(3×3 puzzle) or a hard mode(4×4 puzzle)
・You can play the sliding puzzle of the number immediately, because it is included from the beginning, 
・Let's aim at the best time

I hope you enjoy!